{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BH01313NAM","text":"Nita Caje he woakisni mitawa, o mita Wakan Tanka, na ciksuye ki han he ookiye mitawa. Nikiyela ki han he awacin mitawa nahan tecihila ki han he mita kola. Wowaunsila Nitawa ki he le ounyan nahan ounyan iyokihe nupin ekta woakisni mitawa na wawokiye mitawa numwe. Tuwa Waoh’anpi Owas’in ki, Tuwa lyuha Waslolye ki, Tuwa lyuha.\n\n* Thy name is my healing, O my God, and remembrance of Thee is my remedy. Nearness to Thee is my hope, and love for Thee is my companion. Thy mercy to me is my healing and my succour in both this world and the world to come. Thou, verily, art the All-Bountiful, the All-Knowing, the All-Wise.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"ecbbdf01-d2c2-49a9-bf05-f1caa7bf0fd1","book_cats":{"ceb":{"cat":"Pag-alim","cat_order":10,"order_in_cat":3},"cy":{"cat":"Healing","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":1},"fj":{"cat":"NA VEIVAKABULAI","cat_order":14,"order_in_cat":1},"ha":{"cat":"Neman Lahiya","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":1},"hi":{"cat":"आरोग्य","cat_order":6,"order_in_cat":3},"hu":{"cat":"Gyógyulás","cat_order":15,"order_in_cat":1},"hy":{"cat":"ԱՊԱՔԻՆՈՒՄ","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":1},"hz":{"cat":"Otjiherero: OMBERUKIRO","cat_order":1,"order_in_cat":1},"iba":{"cat":"PENGERAI","cat_order":20,"order_in_cat":2},"ja":{"cat":"治癒ちゆ","cat_order":30,"order_in_cat":5},"ko":{"cat":"원조","cat_order":24,"order_in_cat":1},"ky":{"cat":"ДАБА","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":1},"lb":{"cat":"Heelung a Stäerkt","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":1},"lo":{"cat":"ບົດອະທິຖານຂໍການຮັກສາປິ່ນປົວ","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":1},"mi":{"cat":"MŌ TE WHAKAORA","cat_order":18,"order_in_cat":2},"mn":{"cat":"ӨВЧНӨӨС АНАГААХУЙ","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":1},"ms":{"cat":"KESEMBUHAN","cat_order":22,"order_in_cat":1},"ny":{"cat":"KUCHIRITSA","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":1},"sk":{"cat":"Uzdravenie","cat_order":36,"order_in_cat":2},"sr":{"cat":"ISCELJENJE","cat_order":2,"order_in_cat":2},"srn":{"cat":"Genezing","cat_order":3,"order_in_cat":1},"sw":{"cat":"KUP